  <brief_title>Short vs Long Arm Cast for Distal Radius Fractures: the Verona Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>SLA-Ver</acronym>
  <official_title>Short vs Long Arm Cast for Distal Radius Fractures: the Verona Trial. Randomized Clinical Trial to Assess the Efficacy of Short Arm Cast Versus Long Arm Cast in Conservative Management of Distal Radius Fractures</official_title>
